  "Instructions": "Mix cream cheese and ¾ cup kimchi in a medium bowl.\r\nToss scallions and cilantro in a small bowl to combine. Squeeze in juice from lime, season with salt, and toss again.\r\nSmear kimchi cream cheese over each slice of bread. Top with scallion salad and more kimchi (if using). Drizzle with chili oil; sprinkle with sesame seeds.",
