  "Title": "Creamy Ginger Dressing",
  "Ingredients": "['1/3 cup silken tofu', '1 teaspoon finely grated lemon zest', '2 tablespoons fresh lemon juice', '2 tablespoons unseasoned rice vinegar', '1 teaspoon Dijon mustard', '1 tablespoon coconut palm sugar', '2 tablespoons minced fresh ginger', '1/2 teaspoon minced garlic', '1/4 teaspoon kosher salt', '2 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil', 'Freshly ground white pepper']",
